Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.73,0:00:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.93,0:00:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.40,0:00:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.94,0:00:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.05,0:00:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.26,0:00:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.06,0:00:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.34,0:01:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.78,0:01:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.45,0:01:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.09,0:01:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.79,0:01:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.76,0:01:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團為了統治地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.90,0:01:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以無人操縱MD為主要軍力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創立新生OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.31,0:01:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.44,0:01:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於反對財團的功利主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.94,0:01:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的所有權力被奪去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.48,0:01:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,組織形態出現改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但藉著MD的高性能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.28,0:01:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們快速地擴大了支配地域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.82,0:01:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.69,0:01:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於宇宙衛星認同了財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.56,0:01:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,財團下令殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.83,0:01:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全孤立的鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.90,0:02:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對他們來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.17,0:02:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歷史的洪流繼續不斷倒流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.07,0:02:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克…王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.98,0:02:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然魯莽，但只有這樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.79,0:02:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道很魯莽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.62,0:02:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳叫我桃樂絲就行\N莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.53,0:02:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請妳也叫我莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.03,0:02:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.07,0:02:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下是時代的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為莉莉娜殿下妳是我的偶像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.14,0:02:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十話\N[和莉莉娜的重縫]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.01,0:02:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一分隊前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.12,0:02:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二分隊待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,移動物體反應?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.22,0:02:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各隊部署完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.30,0:03:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左翼有敵機!快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.01,0:03:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[紅色一號]嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.42,0:03:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒理由啊，沒理由啊，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是OZ的內亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強行參戰也只會成為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標嗎? 很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.79,0:03:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有命令要殺死\N和鋼彈的有關的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.50,0:03:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要繼續告訴羅姆斐拉我還生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.93,0:03:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我的抵抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.81,0:03:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.94,0:03:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顯示特列斯派的志氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.28,0:04:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的…\N這樣真的沒問題嗎?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.57,0:04:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充滿野性呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.21,0:04:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸會，希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.01,0:04:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有，卡特爾‧拿巴伯‧溫拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨戰士的樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.49,0:04:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.13,0:04:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙剛才說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你誤會了，我甚麼也沒說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.64,0:04:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想著OZ被消滅就好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.34,0:04:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想過和平的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.81,0:05:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派正迫近這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能動的男人\N就要參加支援部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.96,0:05:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我召集所有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主義嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.83,0:05:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.86,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這地域為了得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.87,0:05:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拒絕參加軍事活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡的特列斯派\N是在舊式政治下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被派駐保衛這國家的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.17,0:05:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們現在變成叛亂份子的反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.21,0:05:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是OZ內部的紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.05,0:05:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我們無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.11,0:05:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是自私的和平主義啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果駐軍妨礙你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.35,0:05:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次就輪到完全和平主義倒下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.09,0:05:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍人保護自己的國民是任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則就會被當作障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.96,0:05:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點也好\N我也想同情特列斯派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但無論如何，戰鬥會開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想在得到和平後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.90,0:05:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才慢慢開始討論啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.17,0:06:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在戰火中，沒有和平主義吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.25,0:06:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.45,0:06:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，我只能袖手旁觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.02,0:06:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你，別介意，這是平常事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.46,0:06:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡亂反抗也只會令糾紛擴大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.26,0:06:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是旅客嗎?   是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.63,0:06:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你實在來到不好的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.27,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來的不是時候\N這裡是個好地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.94,0:06:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了，今次很接近啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.78,0:06:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的艾亞利玆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.49,0:06:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續引敵人過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別忘記進行干擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.44,0:07:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，全力出擊消滅他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.28,0:07:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不向市民發出\N避難警告可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要小看我們的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.95,0:07:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯派的叛亂份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.85,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會在城市前\N消滅他們給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確認戰術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.17,0:07:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主力部隊先攻，引開敵人先鋒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,游擊部隊趁機攻擊，侵入市內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅敵人司令部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.21,0:07:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事成後和主力部隊會合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.91,0:07:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驅逐敵人部隊後，佔據城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,游擊隊的指揮官是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅色一號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你，做得到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.86,0:07:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.46,0:08:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我是鋼彈的駕駛員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.61,0:08:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?有援軍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.54,0:08:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是能令兵力多寡逆轉\N的精銳部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.11,0:08:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從前線調一部份\N過來消滅他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!敵人火力滅弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.56,0:08:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從中央突破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭太自私了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.84,0:08:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無辜的人最可憐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.49,0:09:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果參加這種戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.13,0:09:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就會迷失方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.81,0:09:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在增援來到前解決一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.81,0:09:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒發出避難警告嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅色一號!報告戰況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻陷司令部了嗎?紅色一號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務更改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.13,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎮壓這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.50,0:09:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?你在說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.57,0:09:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，殲滅敵人機動部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接收到敵人無線電通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚…甚麼?   鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.92,0:10:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右前方的里歐\N好像是鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做甚麼?紅色一號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我!紅色一號!紅色一號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.68,0:10:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平民避難確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅色一號叫藍色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.82,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是藍色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.82,0:10:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?紅色一號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何不回應我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.36,0:10:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多處中彈受損
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.12,0:10:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暫時撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.39,0:10:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?紅色一號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.93,0:10:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?有甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我!紅色一號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,紅色一號!怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.32,0:11:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在完全和平的思想之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,軍備是不需要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.79,0:11:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在把這思想傳遍世界之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.29,0:11:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.12,0:11:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不是安全的國家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那種現狀中，這麼快就能和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.03,0:11:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,負起許多國家的未來的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.60,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起學習，我覺得很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一起想出盡快令戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.51,0:11:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這個世上消失的方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好聰明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.91,0:11:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲，妳有意見?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.31,0:11:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果世上的人全是莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.29,0:11:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們就會馬上認為戰鬥是蠢事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.32,0:11:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而戰爭就會從這個世上消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.16,0:11:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N如果大家是莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.83,0:11:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下的長處\N就不會顯眼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.03,0:11:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.33,0:12:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得我的話\N聽來有點虛有其表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但為何要進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家明知是愚蠢行為的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.71,0:12:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得馬上就會有答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.38,0:12:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為我明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥為何不會消失啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.78,0:12:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲，甚麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.45,0:12:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人喜歡戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.85,0:12:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，藉著戰鬥來滿足本能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.46,0:12:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果會有很多人失去性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我對結果沒興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使袖手旁觀\N結果也會出現吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行動非常好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名為戰鬥的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.00,0:12:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是人擁的有最大魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.81,0:12:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類在歷史裡無數次不停戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.14,0:12:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像戰鬥是人類的生存目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.38,0:12:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我這樣想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非不可以戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是一定要戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.39,0:12:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有另一個想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該能避免
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.83,0:13:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在未來重覆過去的歷史悲劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.30,0:13:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭也須要那種聰明的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉著那種人的死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.84,0:13:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歷史會大大地變動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.51,0:13:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.97,0:13:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最終會成為這個時代\N的主要舞台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼回事呢…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲，妳看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.65,0:13:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要我一日活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就會貫徹完全和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.92,0:13:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使我被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.79,0:13:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這主義也會貫徹到底吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.23,0:13:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要害怕死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為死亡是在出生時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經被賜予的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.61,0:13:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，妳放心，莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了妳的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.45,0:13:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常有用的騎士很快就會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.85,0:14:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們一定能保護妳的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.69,0:14:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人裡好像有鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來會為這地域\N帶來嚴重的損毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.17,0:14:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,市長如果堅持完全和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.80,0:14:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，這國家早晚會被滅亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別管，準備戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.28,0:14:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.24,0:14:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.28,0:14:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒事嗎? 我很擔心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.48,0:14:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡要開戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.22,0:14:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我準備暫時離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是新型的MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.94,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一而再 再而三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.04,0:14:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙真喜歡戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.51,0:14:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平比較適合我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個國家有勇氣決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們決定效法山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.68,0:15:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王國?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜殿下，妳沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有甚麼事?柏根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這個戰亂的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倚靠山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.44,0:15:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贊成完全和平主義的國家\N變得很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.41,0:15:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有國家倚靠山克王國作為領袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.81,0:15:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她的負責人有很大的壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.98,0:15:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想即使是莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳也會覺得疲倦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你，柏根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.45,0:15:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但這是我現在的生存意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.36,0:15:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果現在不努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.09,0:15:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為山克王國的君主就沒意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.19,0:15:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，妳的身心也太操勞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直沒時間讓心靈休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲的事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.44,0:15:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柏根，不要說桃樂絲的壞話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.64,0:16:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她究竟在羅姆斐拉\N受過怎樣的教育
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.44,0:16:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,桃樂絲是個聰明的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她或許比我更認真地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.48,0:16:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,思索這個戰爭的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.48,0:16:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想她終有一日會明白我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.72,0:16:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然諾茵小姐\N千叮萬囑要我保密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我認為現在的莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.26,0:16:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有愈多朋友愈好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.87,0:16:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.17,0:16:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼回事?柏根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她查到鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.77,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯的下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛的下落?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.78,0:16:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵小姐現正直接前去見他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.41,0:16:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希…希洛回到地球了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.81,0:16:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他看來也很疲倦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.08,0:16:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵小姐想帶他來山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.36,0:16:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛…會來這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠里歐很難應付啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.12,0:17:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人在最後防衛網交戰中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令部的撤退還未完嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.12,0:17:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.33,0:18:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驚惶失措的只是士兵們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他人很鎮定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.33,0:18:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們已經厭倦戰爭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厭倦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.63,0:18:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.20,0:18:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且有辦法不戰鬥而達至和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.44,0:18:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們選擇了理所當然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.41,0:18:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，許多國家和人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.21,0:18:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始追求完全和平主義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.81,0:18:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然沒有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.05,0:18:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但如果在這個地球上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追求和平的人多過軍人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.28,0:18:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個世界就一定會改變吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽聞山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.12,0:18:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被羅姆斐拉財團定為問題國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為許多國家開始和她結盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.83,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早晚誰也不會再支持羅姆斐拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.97,0:18:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團急於進攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.04,0:18:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是因為他們害怕山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.91,0:18:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全和平主義\N有可能在地球實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老伯，多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.62,0:19:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我的抵抗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.38,0:19:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要比任何人都戰鬥到底…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.98,0:19:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比地球上的任何人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.29,0:19:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比山克王國的莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.66,0:20:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你沒事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.79,0:20:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，我們還不能死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.33,0:20:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們一定要保護山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.37,0:20:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護…山克王國?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.27,0:20:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.30,0:20:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是我們在地球的工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.27,0:20:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.05,0:20:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛鋼彈的能源砲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.65,0:20:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是鋼彈駕駛員\N就知道使用方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.96,0:20:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也會掩護你們逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.21,0:21:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.38,0:21:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎? 你告訴了莉莉娜殿下嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.85,0:21:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，這樣一來鋼彈的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.38,0:21:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就有可能被莉莉娜殿下發覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.62,0:21:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.46,0:21:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柏根，別介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.59,0:21:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是為了那笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.49,0:21:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們今後的辛勞會是值得的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.35,0:22:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.93,0:22:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.93,0:22:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.93,0:22:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.93,0:22:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.43,0:22:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.93,0:23:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.43,0:23:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.93,0:23:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.93,0:23:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.42,0:23:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛和卡特爾投靠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.49,0:23:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜主張完全和平的山克王國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.93,0:23:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那裡絕對不是安居之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.57,0:23:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不斷在世界擴張的和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.94,0:23:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,覺得討厭的羅姆斐拉財團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.77,0:23:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,展開巧妙的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.14,0:23:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，卡特爾，還有諾茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.11,0:23:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保護莉莉娜出擊迎戰
